  News sources still have their purpose! 
</p>
<p>
  Politicians will always spin things to paint themselves in the best light, so I want some third-party analysis. And I’m sure you do too. But, I don’t want to be inundated with all their noise and banter. I want to regulate the flow of information.
</p>
<p>
